      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a fantastic project opportunity! This car is the perfect blank canvas for a restoration enthusiast or someone looking for a valuable source of parts. While it definitely needs a significant amount of mechanical and cosmetic work to get back on the road, it offers a great entry point into the world of car repair at an unbeatable price!",
